Author: babyfaced-bitch
Text: I hope so! I’m kinda freaking out because I had an entire weekend where I was around my family so I was eating a normal amount but since I’ve been on my own again, I’ve been restricting again so hopefully after another week or so, there will be some change

Author: lemonye
Text: Saame. I see no progress even though I’ve been restricting for 2 weeks. But I think it’s that you are used to seeing yourself everyday so the difference is not very drastic. I think after 3-6 weeks we’ll probably see the change!
